{"tid":2113043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃店] 礙於我們店員受到自稱警察襲擊","createTime":"2020-07-17T23:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T00:39:07.000Z","uid":272569,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8b97c741cc13068847493b83437a4b16941f5a79","tid":2113043,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://is.gd/vnC8dh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FvnC8dh&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=3935d784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/vnC8dh</a><br />\n<br />\n礙於我們店員受到自稱警察襲擊<br />\n<br />\n今次搵利器/ 化學物磨損手部<br />\n<br />\n同日亦在暗角襲擊他頭部<br />\n<br />\n希望警方可以盡快作出一個合理交代<br />\n<br />\n為何我店裏同事沒有犯事，沒有吸毒<br />\n<br />\n日日如常放工，為何會受到如此對待？<br />\n<br />\n同事得18歲仔<br />\n<br />\n事發過咗一段時間問返佢當時情況佢會腳震同埋手震<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n希望2名自稱警員可以盡快自首<br />\n<br />\n根據同事形容身體特徵<br />\n<br />\n- 脾氣暴躁<br />\n- 戴佛牌<br />\n- all black頭<br />\n- MK<br />\n- 全身服裝黑<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我只可形容今次事件係痴撚線，呀仔嗰日7月15（星期三）放工淨係去咗CGA夾公仔，夾完公仔離開大門時就被兩名警員伏擊<br />\n<br />\n我自己百份百相信同事品格冇問題先會俾佢喺舖頭做野，唔吸毒冇犯罪記錄，日日盡力幫手整機<br />\n<br />\n但你班暴力狂就連細路仔都蝦！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4b1RUp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4b1RUp.jpg&h=fdcbf02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3C一直比黑警攪，希望附近手足留意下，<br />\n早排先比人偷嘢 <a href=\"https://is.gd/K2ecBU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FK2ecBU&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=b48a9e93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/K2ecBU</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUivLfA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUivLfA.jpg&h=f7d5cda6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做到咁明顯，所以邊個會信無殺人強姦輪姦毀屍滅跡同被自殺？"},{"pid":"e45bce40c4b945037a227884429f28927a5039b2","tid":2113043,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:06:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fac920a9c51caef4266b8e891c4c1c586f534ace","tid":2113043,"uid":82974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:09:22.000Z","msg":"香港警察，香港最大犯罪集團"},{"pid":"756f6620d94b662a755f69d6d0d6fa50aec62302","tid":2113043,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c347da2fb7a776b22971cf5f7fca3b1667fbe8","tid":2113043,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:15:16.000Z","msg":"撚樣狗"},{"pid":"fcecd7faa85e0371f58f10623ce8c3d6bb035c56","tid":2113043,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac920a9c51caef4266b8e891c4c1c586f534ace","tid":2113043,"uid":82974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:09:22.000Z","msg":"香港警察，香港最大犯罪集團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:17:23.000Z","msg":"係 世界最大有牌犯罪集團，勁過意大利黑手黨"},{"pid":"36bd952c16dbc497ef577774b3800368438b5458","tid":2113043,"uid":211484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:18:01.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a1e207c102cb0279288e3e9aac925f50fc7b51bf","tid":2113043,"uid":40521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGJOBMw.png&amp;h=731371ce&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"19